data.text:
Through the Bible With Les Feldick

Les Feldick was an Oklahoma farmer and rancher with a special gift for teaching the Bible. His simple and nondenominational approach on the program "Through the Bible with Les Feldick" has reached millions around the world with the Gospel of Grace.

Joyce Meyer Enjoying Everyday Life Galatians New

In Christ, believers learn to live their lives in a whole new way; Joyce teaches from the book of Galatians how to let go of the old.

Signs & Secrets of the Messiah with Rabbi Jason Sobel The Signs and Secrets of Healing (Part 1)

A man laid by the pool of Bethesda for 38 years, waiting for healing; in an instant Yeshua changed the man's entire life; Rabbi Jason explores the significance of where and when this miracle took place, and what that means for lives today.
